* all functions which return errno_t should return real errno, not
  just -1.

* should we have reset method in object plugins? is call like
  seek(obj, 0) will not be convenient enough?

* should we split reiser4_fs_create and reiser4_fs_open onto separate
  functions?

* reiser4_joint_realize may be improved by rid of search_by_key

* move the all common code of reg40 and dir40 plugins to separate
  file.

* node print method for printing the all node items

* finish balancing code in node40 plugin.

* reg40_layout, which will allow us to measure the fragmentation of
  the regular files

* --print-journal and --print-alloc options in debugfs.

* FIBMAP ioctl implementation in reiser4

* --data-fragmentation option in debugfs.reiser4

* fix checksum calculating for the last block of bitmap
